# Dalit Archive Scrapers

This project processes the URLs in `list.txt` one by one using `scrapling`.

## Setup

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
.venv/bin/pip install -e '.[dev]'
```

## Usage

Run every configured source in `list.txt`:

```bash
.venv/bin/dalit-scrapers run-all
```

Run one configured source by its URL:

```bash
.venv/bin/dalit-scrapers run-one --url 'https://www.epw.in/search?epw_input=dalit'
```

Verify the latest saved output for one source:

```bash
.venv/bin/dalit-scrapers verify-one --url 'https://www.epw.in/search?epw_input=dalit'
```

Outputs are written under `output/<source_id>/`.
